Package lab5.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddCommand
    "add" command, add SpaceMarine instance in collection
    AddIfMaxCommand
    "add_if_max" command, add item in collection if item bigger than max element in collection
    AverageOfHealthCommand
    "average_health" command, print average health value in collection
    ClearCommand
    "clear" command, clear whole collection
    Command
    Abstract class for all commands
    ExecuteScriptCommand
    "execute" command, script execution
    ExitCommand
    "exite" command, end of work program
    HelpCommand
    "help" command, print list of available command and description
    InfoCommand
    "info" command, print info about command
    PrintFieldDescendingChapterCommand
    "print_chapter" command, Print descending chapter's fields
    PrintUniqueHealthCommand
    "print_unique_health" command, print uniq health values
    RemoveByIdCommand  
    RemoveFirstCommand
    "remove_first" command, remove first element in collection
    RemoveLowerCommand
    "remove_lower" command, remove elements which lower than current
    SaveCommand
    "save" command, save whole collection in file (json format)
    ShowCommand
    "show" command, show whole elements from collection
    UpdateIdCommand
    "update" command, update collection item by id
